@UnitConversion_HostAddress = http://localhost:5053

### List supported categories and units
GET {{UnitConversion_HostAddress}}/api/v1/categories
Accept: application/json

###

### Convert kilometers to miles
POST {{UnitConversion_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Conversion
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "length",
  "fromUnit": "kilometers",
  "toUnit": "miles",
  "value": 1
}

###

### Convert Celsius to Fahrenheit
POST {{UnitConversion_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Conversion
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "temperature",
  "fromUnit": "celsius",
  "toUnit": "fahrenheit",
  "value": 100
}

###

### Health check
GET {{UnitConversion_HostAddress}}/health

###
